Your enemies in this war are demons, but are you sure about that? 
Experience a game when you uses your rifle and the skill of stop the time to fight your enemies in this warfare!
Another Warfare is a 2d platformer shooter, but here, time moves only when you move.[h2]Featuring:[/h2][list][li]Stylized pixel-art;
[/li][li]30+ [b]hand-crafted levels[/b] with increasing complexity;
[/li][li]A shooter game with a [b]stunning and polished[/b] game feel;
[/li][li]Enjoy the  dangers of the Another Warfare;[/li][/list]
